name: UfoConqueror
description:
Skills Finland Finals Winner 2021

Conquer land by running over a line that you leave behind while you move forward constantly. 

Collect abilities to make you faster, gain energy back or confuse your enemy!

Cover the most area with your own colour before time runs out!
